ivardefs.name: datasetId
ivardefs.desc: Id of the variant in this external repository. The server will understand how to use this id to call for more info about datasets in external repository.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: URI of an external repository which contains further details about the genetics data.

ivardefs.name: readsetId
ivardefs.desc: Id of the read in this external repository.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: Click and see / RESTful API / Need login to see / RESTful API with authentication / Other ways to see resource.

ivardefs.name: url
ivardefs.desc: URI of an external repository which contains further details about the genetics data.

ivardefs.name: variantsetId
ivardefs.desc: Id of the variantset in this external repository. The server will understand how to use this id to call for more info about variantsets in external repository.

properties.desc: Configurations of the external repository. The repository shall store target's observedSeq or records related with target's observedSeq.
